dct_title_s: New York State map : four sheet, 1:250,000. South sheet
dct_description_sm: New York State. Department of Transportation. Explanatory text: 28p. Transverse Mercator projection, (NYTM) grid. Shows administrative divisions and Indian Reservations. Cover title of accompanying gazetteer: Four sheet 1:250,000 scale New York State map gazetteer. One map in four sheets.
